    "schema:description": "Metadata harvested from BCO-DMO by the EarthCube GeoCodes catalog using Gleaner. Converted to CDIF Core profile: Property names prefixed with schema: namespace; @context converted to CDIF prefix declarations (schema, dcterms, dcat, prov); @type values normalized to arrays with schema: prefix; schema:dateModified set from datePublished; Distributions normalized (encodingFormat arrays, @type, contentUrl); schema:creator wrapped in @list; schema:provider wrapped in array; spatialCoverage normalized to array of Place objects; schema:keywords split from comma-separated string to array. Round 2 fixes: Funding funder @type changed from FundingAgency to Organization (FundingAgency not in CDIF schema). Moved to Discovery: Added conformsTo discovery/1.0; temporalCoverage wrapped in array; variableMeasured alternateName values wrapped in arrays."
